" d - i-v-o-r-c-e " is an american country music song written by bobby braddock and curly putman , and made famous by tammy wynette .

albums : ( hi , i 'm lorrie morgan )   i recorded " you and me " for a 1998 tribute album to this late legend ; rosanne cash contributed " d - i-v-o-r-c-e "

